## LAME MP3 Encoder

DeChaff bundles a pre-compiled binary of LAME (Lame Ain't an MP3 Encoder),
which is licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License, version 2.0
or later (LGPL v2.0+).

LAME source code is available at: https://lame.sourceforge.io

In accordance with the LGPL, you are free to replace the bundled LAME binary
with a modified version of your own. The LAME binary is re-signed at build
time via the Xcode build phase "Re-sign bundled lame with Hardened Runtime"
— replace the binary at DeChaff/lame and re-run that phase to link against
your own build.

The full text of the GNU Lesser General Public License v2.0 is available at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/old-licenses/lgpl-2.0.html
